meta {
  name: Track order
  type: http
  seq: 4
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  X-User-Id: {{userId}}
}

docs {
  Re-send until `status` is COMPLETED — the saga takes a few seconds to run through
  reserve → pay → accept → courier → deliver → capture. For live updates, a WebSocket
  client can `track` the same orderId instead of polling.
}
